Title: Geometries of orthogonal groups and their contractions

classical deformation viewpointAuthors: Mariano Santander and Francisco J. Herranz

Comments: 9 pages, LaTeX; contribution presented by M.Santander to the II

International Workshop on Classical and Quantum Integrible Systems (Dubna,8-12 July,1996), to be published in Int.J.Mod.Phys.ARings and AlgebrasJournal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A12 (1997) 99-108

The geometries of spaces having as groups the real orthogonal groups and someof their contractions are described from a common point of view. Their centralextensions and Casimirs are explicitly given. An approach to the trigonometryof their spaces is also advanced.